<h3 id="forecasted-balance">Forecasted balance</h3>
<p>The <em>forecasted balance</em> is the amount of leave available on a future date. Accruals and carry-forward adjustments are forecasted up to that date.</p>
<p>Human Resources uses the following formula:</p>
<p>Monday forecasted balance = Current balance – Requests + Accruals – Carry-forward adjustment</p>
